# markup: rd

= Revision history for cyclops

== 0.3.0 [2018-06-16]

* <b>Dropped support for Ruby 2.0.</b>
* Dropped +safe_yaml+ dependency in favour of standard library.

== 0.2.0 [2015-10-02]

* Extracted Cyclops#open_file and Cyclops#open_std from
  Cyclops#open_file_or_std so they can be overwritten in subclasses.

== 0.1.0 [2014-11-26]

* Extracted Cyclops#config_present? from Cyclops#config_opts so it can be
  overwritten in subclasses.

== 0.0.4 [2014-09-01]

* Added support for <tt>--[no-]<switch></tt>.
* <tt>--verbose</tt> also prints program name and version.
* Print error and usage on parse errors.

== 0.0.3 [2014-04-14]

* Always set symbol key in options hash.

== 0.0.2 [2014-04-12]

* Prevent Cyclops::VERSION from clobbering Subclass::VERSION.
* Fixed error in OptionParser convenience methods.

== 0.0.1 [2014-04-11]

* First release (extracted from ruby-nuggets).
* Added some OptionParser convenience methods.

== 0.0.0 [2014-04-11]

* Birthday :-)
